{"tid":288174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"十年釣魚心得分享","createTime":"2017-06-18T04:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T09:08:00.000Z","uid":1453,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b56d18ae38d0b02c5b15acfb670e91d6268dcaf","tid":288174,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"我既心得係。唔使買桿既 <br />\n<br />\n一個八磅魚排。一包鈎。一袋鉛。兩條蟲。一把刀。夠玩半日 <br />\n<br />\n首先執齊以上裝備。去七仔買半打藍妹。 <br />\n行過街市斬半隻燒鵝。 <br />\n<br />\n去就近碼頭霸個靚位。 <br />\n<br />\n隊罐啤食隻脾先 <br />\n<br />\nD骨就掉落海引d魚 <br />\n之後就開壇落鉛幫鈎。一條蟲切十份 <br />\n咁你就有廿份餌。 <br />\n之後就掉落海等。當然。過程中不忘隊啤食燒鵝同隔離d釣友吹水。吹得幾個字一扯！ <br />\n<br />\nOk kick石！ <br />\n<br />\n扯斷收返上黎又綁過。 <br />\n如是者十次八次用晒你d鉛同埋鈎之後。你d啤酒同燒鵝都所餘無幾（骨照舊掉落海引魚） <br />\n咁你就可以食埋隻鵝，飲埋罐藍妹，執埋d垃圾。有剩d蟲就比隔離or掉落海。 <br />\n之後拎返個冇左一半絲既魚排 <br />\n返去同屋企人講 <br />\n「刁。今日（落雨/冇落雨/大太陽/冇太陽）。成個海都冇魚 。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef6afbff1c934d70f6403c09a25d18ce75bcde9","tid":288174,"uid":33843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"拉B"},{"pid":"c22c204a64356e56f8fb1dce337dd3f0bdda4bab","tid":288174,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉B</blockquote><br />\n拔萃有個大仆街<br />\n佢個名叫陳庭佳<br />\n陳庭佳"},{"pid":"e1b2a47468b3f213f11f9d7f1d65ca91d7d2fb6f","tid":288174,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"8117242a08d0c5e76c212d044a97c3402b7ff30f","tid":288174,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hi</blockquote><br />\nhi rubbish"},{"pid":"8c9e70cc9ebcc5116bfd7c235259969e9c7a943e","tid":288174,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"5分鷹"},{"pid":"d24a139a71f87aa0d134bddfd8cb3c80f941948a","tid":288174,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim